metadata.name: FALLING APART
metadata.description:
FALLING APART is my first ever fully on chain 1:1 art. Breaking new boundaries for the absolute permanence of my art existing on the Blockchain. 

FALLING APART is inspired by regret and closure. Something that can often feel so close, yet is hard to grasp.
